main.description: With an interest in Cloud Computing, UI/UX Design, and Network Security, I hope to expand my software engineering knowledge.  With a keen interest in photography, I spend my time tinkling with Photoshop and Lightroom while being an avid progammer.
main.bio: With a passion in Computer Science, I volunteer with non-profit organizations to bring STEM to underprivileged communities. With my previous experience as a coding instructor, I understand the teaching and learning aspect of computer science. By learning how to use the Google Cloud platform, I have developed an interest in cloud computing.
